{"tid":1623454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車手青馬橋安全車速","createTime":"2019-10-04T22:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T01:02:54.000Z","uid":279848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"49eff4538527687dca946a8c3e3d96468f2a8bfe","tid":1623454,"uid":279848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:13:15.000Z","msg":"召集有車嘅手足<br />\n空車<br />\n唔好有任何gear<br />\n响青馬<br />\n注意安全駕駛<br />\n今朝港鐵全線停機<br />\n機場快線都冧咗"},{"pid":"66fa3f017bd3d2057c835ce2f1931c2a024de510","tid":1623454,"uid":299104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:17:11.000Z","msg":"由緊急法可以睇得出，政府真係好驚我地好似10&middot;1咁搞多鍋。所以我地一定要吃著上，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連續一個星期流水式18區開花</strong></span>，就算凌晨都唔可以停，真正咁耗盡班狗嘅狗力。等佢地唔可以執行緊急法。<br />\n<br />\n對家只有三萬人，就算加埋d武警老解最多都係五萬人，而我地至少有二十萬勇武+170萬和理非，我地人多一班人打完要休息，可以有另外一班人頂上去，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>流水式咁同班狗打</strong></span>，做到真正嘅疲敵戰術。<br />\n<br />\n班狗絕對頂唔住我地多區連續一個星期嘅攻勢，由「10&middot;1」戰役可以睇到，班狗可以分散嘅狗力已經不足，各區都露出破綻，逼到佢只可以開實彈。計下數，班狗12小時輪班，若果高強度工作10個鐘，再翻狗竇休足12個鐘都唔一定能完全恢復精力，之後又同佢玩10個鐘，連續咁1個星期，加埋d gear咁重，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地心理同生理上肯定頂唔順，失守防線，最後自爆</span>。<br />\n<br />\n反惡法，民怨沸騰，各位手足要吃住個勢上，行動升級，還我們真正的香港。我倡議，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10月7號到14號全港三罷，各區接力開花</strong></span>。例個週末大家做好文宣，下個星期錫佢春袋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"270839802662a0e800b9dcd2a43ad77f2dc0435e","tid":1623454,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:23:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cd0543fea95a6304c2eafe6e4b97c8e658c75b9","tid":1623454,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:23:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d657e2ef7df94d4aab2dc426658fbe4ac3876517","tid":1623454,"uid":24296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:30:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"a0f9125526aa38dc33bedfb550aa40d8b0178f11","tid":1623454,"uid":297561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"青馬已經塞到停哂係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65fc4f59098b85facf9c5b827050a353c93aece","tid":1623454,"uid":278786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:29:19.000Z","msg":"[禁蒙面法之破解］合法蒙面 + 拆解背後陰謀 + 策略應對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1623533/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1623533/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"989c277c0c5e7edb8e0c99fa4923e3377d7a0c8b","tid":1623454,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"機場巴士只係比平時用多一倍時間就入到機場<br />\n利申，今日飛"},{"pid":"540332bcc5017139b5fda15b1b3cb521cfc0bced","tid":1623454,"uid":130044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"64991f058d94e44a2f4b1d08b2d49e96c1d173e7","tid":1623454,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}